      "value": "<p><em>Biome: Plains</em></p>\n<p>The plant has a tuberous root, and large purplish flowers with yellow-red centers. The pistils of the flower must be pulped into a paste which is then left to dry for a week. The resulting powder is taken as snuff. This herb raises all attribute scores by one for one hour. After consumption the first time, the user must make a DC 18 Constitution Save or become addicted. After the initial hour of stat raises, stats will lower from the base value by 1 every day until the next consumption.</p>",
